getNodeName

public String getNodeName()
Description copied from interface: IPSCmsComponent
The name of the element returned by the toXml and expected by the fromXml methods. Typically, this should be of the form: if the base class name is 'PSFoo', then this method should return 'PSXFoo'.

Specified by:
